title: Dream Coaching with Tara Kirby
description: Are you ready to create clarity, build confidence, and make cash through your business? Tara Kirby helps entrepreneurs do all 3 with her wildly successful DREAM Method coaching. Tara has done and seen it all. Through her extensive entrepreneurial journey, Tara was helping others succeed in their businesses but wanted to see that same type of success for herself. After quitting everything and pulling back for 6 months, Tara developed the DREAM Method Coaching which teaches female entrepreneurs how they can have the business, the babies, and the beach house!
